Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.39,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,0)}口ずさめたら
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.72,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,きいて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.97,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,世界がほどける音が
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.97,0:02:49.39,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,かけてくる
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.73,OP-JPN,,0,0,0,,かけてくる
