Dialogue: 7,0:08:56.95,0:08:57.89,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,朝
Dialogue: 8,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,绘美理
Dialogue: 7,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.39,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,えみり
